title: Newspring Worship
description:
A compilation of NewSpring Albums and Live recordings that I've pieced together in top-of-the-line 320kbps MP3 format. I go to NewSpring Church and really enjoy every bit of music they produce, and I hope you will too. :)



Here's a list of the Albums:

-A Matchlight in the Dark

-Gauntlet 2012 Live EP

-Gauntlet 2013 Live EP

-No Other Name

-Our God Is Love

-The Hour

And like I said they're all in 320 kbps and in MP3 audio format, and all for only half a gigabyte! It's because I Love you guys. Have a blessed Day.

Sincerely,

Encrypt3d
